channel.title: HELP js5 connect problem when server's online? HELP
channel.description: Well, today, I was playing my server and editing it in the files. Also, I went into NPCspawn, I deleted some NPC's that kinda lagged my server. They were legend guards saying my servers name and I didn't want so many. So I deleted some from the NPCspawn.java notepad, and i saved, compiled. So then I ran the server, thinking everything's fine. I opened up my client and it got stuck at connecting to update server. The client prompt thing said error_js5connect thing. But, I turned on the server. So now my client won't connect to my server. And help? Thanks.
